high_descs: Take a few steps front to reach the bed.
Table a keychain from the bed
Turn towards your right and walk few steps right and stand before the box.
Put the keychain in the cardboard box which is behind the pillow.
Take the box from the bed.
Turn back and walk towards the right side corner of the room to reach the desk.
Put the cardboard box along with the key next to the desk.
anns.task_desc: Put the KeyChain along with the Box next to the Desk

high_descs: Head towards the bed.
Pick up the keychain on the bed.
Turn to the box to your right and then turn left towards the bed.
Put the keychain in the box behind the pillow on the bed.
Pick up the box with the key chain on the bed.
Turn around, go straight and then head towards the lamp on the desk to your left.
Put the box with the key chain on the desk beside the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Placing the KeyChain inside the Box on the Desk.

high_descs: walk towards the bed in the bedroom
Pick up the keychain off of the bed.
turn around and then back towards the box.
Grab the keychain at the back of the bed.
Set the keys inside the box.
turn around towards the brown desk.
Set the box down on the brown desk.
anns.task_desc: Move the KeyChain into a Box on the brown Desk.
